[2026-06-13]  CUSTOM CURSOR — DESKTOP ONLY + SMOOTH
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 - components/ui/CursorGlow.tsx: rewritten.
     * Renders ONLY on desktop (matchMedia "(hover:hover) and (pointer:fine)").
       On mobile / tablet (touch) it no longer renders at all — fixes the
       stray cyan dot that previously sat in the corner on touch devices.
     * Smoothness: pointer tracked in a ref (no React re-render per move) and
       eased toward the target every frame via requestAnimationFrame —
       dot lerp 0.35 (fast), ring lerp 0.16 (trailing). Uses translate3d +
       will-change-transform for GPU-accelerated, buttery motion.
 - app/globals.css: removed global `cursor: none` from body; now applied only
   inside `@media (hover:hover) and (pointer:fine)`. Touch devices keep normal
   behavior. Added -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent.

